    <div class="statement">
      Magically convert your photoshop files to HTML <span class="ampersand">&</span> CSS.
    </div>


    <div class="row features-block">
      <div class="span6 features"> 
        <ul>
          <li class="first">Get clean code in minutes</li>
          <li>No absolute positioning, no website-as-images.</li>
          <li>Minimal, maintainable markup</li>
          <li>Uses Compass+SASS for maintainable CSS</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="span3 try-block">
        <a href="/designs?fv=1" class="start-using-button">Try now</a>
        <em> We use Google auth to notify your uploads. We won't spam you. </em>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="viral container">
    <div class="viral-inner">
      <%= render 'shared/snippets/gplusone' %>
      <%= render 'shared/snippets/tweet' %>
      <%= render 'shared/snippets/fbshare' %>
    </div>
  </div>
